{"tid":2053123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[push到上熱門] 國際戰線新手教學：Twitter篇","createTime":"2020-06-06T04:30:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T15:51:26.000Z","uid":229502,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"a5bc6e06445f1a98127792d782729629a574184f","tid":2053123,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T04:30:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(上兩個po推唔起，今次再試推唔推到)</span></span><br />\n<br />\n喺本地戰線之外，其實國際戰線都好重要，國際線可以幫我哋爭取國際民意，當民意夠大嘅時候，更可以將原本奶共嘅國家轉軚，形成全球反共聯合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但無奈有好多香港人都唔識用Twitter同Reddit之類外國人好常用嘅社交媒體，今日等我教大家用Twitter<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>申請Twitter Aacount</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://其實上Twitter.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%85%B6%E5%AF%A6%E4%B8%8ATwitter.com&d=bCxsXTpKmrqj5N4FYztdx5tjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=4aa7d70b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://其實上Twitter.com</a>就可以搵到掣申請！如果用電話嘅可以用Twitter app或者去<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/explore/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fexplore%2F&d=bCxsXTpKmrqj5N4FYztdx5tjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=de02b256\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/explore/</a> ，會見到有option (<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hxUs1iB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhxUs1iB.jpg&h=d59c88a9&s={SIZE}\" />)<br />\n<br />\n㩒咗入去之後，可以揀用電話或者Email申請，我當然提議大家用Email，個名如果你唔怕風險可以打真名，驚嘅求其作就得 (<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jGnN1ji.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjGnN1ji.jpg&h=0f2fa2ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xLQG5LZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxLQG5LZ.jpg&h=81887d95&s={SIZE}\" />)<br />\n<br />\n打完之後佢會問你畀唔畀佢track你，一樣唔驚就畀，驚就唔好畀  (<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YRWK3yp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYRWK3yp.jpg&h=7b2bf232&s={SIZE}\" />)<br />\n<br />\n跟住就可以註冊喇 (<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3wUAqNc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3wUAqNc.jpg&h=a72fd533&s={SIZE}\" />)<br />\n<br />\n跟住佢會send verification code畀你 (<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mdAcs0Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmdAcs0Z.jpg&h=358ae183&s={SIZE}\" />)<br />\n<br />\n跟住打密碼，記得要set得安全啲，我試過打完國際線之後有不明人士試過想登入我account <br />\n<br />\n之後佢會叫你加profile相 (求其set)，自己嘅description (話自己乜乜乜就得)，同埋你感興趣嘅嘢。<br />\n<br />\n感興趣嘅嘢方面你可以揀啲自己真係有興趣嘅嘢同埋關國際線嘅嘢，起碼唔好畀人覺得你係bot。<br />\n<br />\n跟住佢會suggest啲嘢畀你follow，一樣follow返手足同自己有興趣嘅嘢，咁人哋一出Tweet你就會收到(<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GwrbJA5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGwrbJA5.jpg&h=fbd87e93&s={SIZE}\" />)<br />\n <br />\n之後佢問你開唔開notification ，我提議開因為手足一出post你就知 (<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jWF0BWF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjWF0BWF.jpg&h=eb17b907&s={SIZE}\" />)<br />\n<br />\n跟住如果你係手機website版佢會問你用唔用app，我覺得用app好啲<br />\n<br />\n<strong>你已經成功申請Account！</strong><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/06/05/144307_8646f6379c9bd5c61874dd4db5712ecc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F06%2F05%2F144307_8646f6379c9bd5c61874dd4db5712ecc.jpg&h=d6539363&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Twitter 基本知識</ins></strong><br />\n我用呢幅圖 (其中一位手足嘅圖) 嚟講解下Twitter嘅元素<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BLOQZcf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBLOQZcf.jpg&h=f4c5876d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTweet: <span style=\"color: red;\">即係post，但係喺Twitter上面一定唔好叫post，而係Tweet，如果你講post人哋可能會對你反感，你當約定俗成記咗佢就得<br />\n</span><br />\n人名(User): 即係你嗰Account嘅名，通常係代表你個人或者組織嘅目的<br />\n使用者名稱(username): 同人名唔通，Username係下面@xxxxx嘅嘢，通常亂改都得，但係平時人哋search嘢或者Tag人都係用Username (好似侵嘅@RealDonaldTrump)，所以好嘅Username係可以令人認到你。<br />\nHashtag: 當一個Hashtag畀人用嘅次數夠多，佢就會上Trend (好似註冊完成幅圖咁)，上Trend之後啲人都會見到個hashtag，所以打國際線應該將嗰日主題嘅Hashtag盡力衝上Trend，咁先會多人留意<br />\nRetweet/Like人數/Like：唔使講。<br />\nComment: 通常你Comment有兩種，一個係Retweet+Comment，一個係Comment，Retweet+Comment唔會幫到個Tweet boost到上去，所以大家應該Retweet還Retweet，Comment還Comment，通常你Comment加多張圖Reach會多啲，咩係Reach陣間會講<br />\nRetweet: <span style=\"color: red;\">即係share，但同Tweet一樣，要講Retweet 而唔係Share，原因一樣。</span><br />\n<br />\n呢啲就係你要識嘅Twitter基本Interface知識喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實打國際線真係好重要，但係得幾百或者幾千人打，試想如果有幾萬人或者幾十萬人，左翼都唔會頂得住人海攻勢而要幫我哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(但大家都要打先得)，政客會更加睇到香港人嘅需求，過法案都過得快啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n空間唔夠，下面補充"},{"pid":"706155518606556b94071e69c0edb29bd7ca8ded","tid":2053123,"uid":229502,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T04:32:32.000Z","msg":"跟住我教大家點出Tweet: <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3YgnQoh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3YgnQoh.jpg&h=847cc89a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下面有四樣嘢<br />\n<br />\n由左至右第一個係加圖，唔使解釋<br />\n<br />\n第二個係加GIF:㩒咗之後可以search啲出名嘅GIF嚟用 (<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FYoaeQB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFYoaeQB.jpg&h=9019d016&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n)<br />\n<br />\n第三個係poll:即係有時外國議員問我哋睇法都係用依個，最多可以set期限去7日 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AMo15Xv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAMo15Xv.jpg&h=ede4062a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第四個係Schedule，例如可以提返人幾時到69，612之類<br />\n<br />\nMain Content梗係注重返幫香港，或者整好個profile嗰陣可以講下日常生活之類<br />\n<br />\n加#Hashtag嘅好處同意義同用法上面講咗<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>仲有一樣嘢叫Reach</ins></strong><br />\nReach顧名思義即係觸及人數，代表喺Twitter上面有幾多個人睇到你個Tweet: <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PmJNg48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPmJNg48.jpg&h=73ce6e02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上面有中文咩意思我諗大家都明，所以我哋出Tweet係要諗辦法增加Reach<br />\n<br />\n------------------------------<br />\n你依家已經識用Twitter，我提議你用以下幾個途徑知道嗰日國際線要打咩<br />\n<br />\nTelegram: @TwitterHelpBot，每日都有新Task，得閒可以做，仲有得睇排行榜<br />\n香城Online: 唔單止Twitter，連Reddit，連登，行動，黃店都有，其實真係極好用<br />\n各種Telegram Channel: 唔方便po link，睇下搵唔搵到<br />\nTwitter 手足： 最基本嘅方法就係睇手足Tweet乜就Tweet乜"},{"pid":"51a3b23badc656fae29c23d4dea6097470fa02e5","tid":2053123,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T04:37:07.000Z","msg":"又冇人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f67bf7ed2be1d531fbf32c24dfeaaab373e66dd9","tid":2053123,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T04:38:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67a30926915dc0f4e220da9b78f3f0537068171b","tid":2053123,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T04:41:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"277da7ffdfd1b74458609ed21e2e36ef8917a2e2","tid":2053123,"uid":124860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T05:27:35.000Z","msg":"手快禁錯負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推"},{"pid":"f57163328a08c7e35094def9fabe1abf68d0b53b","tid":2053123,"uid":35090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T05:29:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f5f94e1059bcb5fa88b6dbf5418afc1c459dbbb","tid":2053123,"uid":205763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T05:43:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"979567094bcd52102c995396ac9c0a5d4b2e079c","tid":2053123,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"277da7ffdfd1b74458609ed21e2e36ef8917a2e2","tid":2053123,"uid":124860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T05:27:35.000Z","msg":"手快禁錯負皮<img src